<body>
Reports a CSS class reference in the <a href="https://github.com/css-modules/css-modules#composition">'composes'</a>
rule that cannot be resolved to any valid target.
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code>
  .className {/* ... */}

  .otherClassName {
    composes: className;
  }
</code></pre>
<!-- tooltip end -->
